sub_title: Honorary Consul , Inspirational Speaker, Entrepreneur, Investor, Gender Sensitive Programming Expert
summary:
A result-driven, solution-oriented, with international expertise in gender sensitive programming and monitoring, cross-cultural communication, investment, public policies , migration and community development.

Humanitarian at heart, Mutesa strongly believes that helping people is not done through handouts but by empowering communities through promoting business and entrepreneurship.

She considers herself as an Afro-realist and an activist who has chosen fighting poverty as a way to advocate for justice for all.
